@startuml CourseEnrollmentDeployment
title Course registration and enrollment — deployment diagram

skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
  BorderColor #333333
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #333333
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor #FFF8E7
  BorderColor #333333
}

node "End user device" as Device {
  artifact "Web browser" as Browser
}

node "Frontend hosting" as FrontHost <<execution environment>> {
  artifact "Static SPA\n(Vite production build)" as SPA
  note bottom of SPA
    Serves HTML/JS/CSS.
    **VITE_API_URL** points at the API origin.
  end note
}

node "Backend hosting" as ApiHost <<execution environment>> {
  artifact "REST API\n(Node 20+ · Fastify)" as API
  note bottom of API
    Env: **DATABASE_URL**, **JWT_SECRET**,
    **CLIENT_ORIGIN** (SPA origin(s) for CORS).
  end note
}

database "PostgreSQL" as DB <<managed DB>>
cloud "Object storage\n(optional)" as Blob <<Vercel Blob>>

Browser --> SPA : HTTPS\n(load UI)
Browser --> API : HTTPS\n(JSON + cookies / Bearer)

API --> DB : SQL\n(pooled TLS)
API --> Blob : HTTPS\n(student PDFs,\nwhen configured)

@enduml
